<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="K_6656" type="Brief"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>Pasquale Veladini an Alfred Escher, Lugano, Montag, 25. Mai 1868</title></titleStmt><publicationStmt><p>Digitale Briefedition Alfred Escher, Zürich: Alfred Escher-Stiftung.</p></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><msDesc><msIdentifier><institution>SBB Historic</institution><idno>VGB_GB_SBBGB01_010</idno></msIdentifier></msDesc><bibl type="printed"/></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><textClass><keywords scheme="http://briefedition.alfred-escher.ch/keywords"><term>Gotthardbahnprojekt</term><term>Eisenbahnstrecken Konzessionen</term></keywords></textClass><correspDesc><correspAction type="sent"><persName key="Veladini Pasquale" type="addressee">Pasquale Veladini</persName><persName key="Escher (vom Glas) Alfred" type="sender">Alfred Escher</persName><placeName>Lugano</placeName><date when="1868-05-25">25. Mai 1868</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><placeName>Zürich</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="previous" target="B4080"/><ref type="next" target="B4081"/><ref type="next-in-corresp" target="B7947"/><ptr type="context" target="6656 7947 5745"/></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><front>
      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_6656_p1"><lb xml:id="p1-l1"/>
          <choice><abbr>Sig.</abbr><expan>Signore (Herr)</expan></choice>
          <choice><abbr>Cons.</abbr><expan>Consigliere (Ratsmitglied)</expan></choice> Alfredo Escher <lb xml:id="p1-l2"/><placeName key="Zürich (Stadt)">Zurigo</placeName>.</p>
      </div>
      <div type="dateline">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_6656_p2"><lb xml:id="p1-l3"/>
          <placeName key="Lugano">Lugano</placeName>
          <date when="1868-05-25">25 Maggio 1868</date>.</p>
      </div>
    </front><body>
      <p rend="left" xml:id="K_6656_p3"><lb xml:id="p1-l4"/>Sino dal primo suscitarsi qui il progetto di chiedere
				<lb xml:id="p1-l5"/>una concessione del tronco di ferrovia <placeName key="Chiasso">Chiasso</placeName> –
				<lb xml:id="p1-l6"/><hi rend="underline"><placeName key="Lugano">Lugano</placeName></hi>, verbo scritto ai <choice><abbr>sig<hi rend="sup">ri</hi> </abbr><expan>signori (Herren)</expan></choice> <persName key="Zingg Josef">Zingg</persName> e
				<lb xml:id="p1-l7"/><persName key="Koller Gottlieb">Koller-Burckardt</persName><note type="transcript">sic!</note>, informandoli del fatto, e
				<lb xml:id="p1-l8"/>per averne instruzioni.
			</p>
      <p rend="left" xml:id="K_6656_p4"><lb xml:id="p1-l9"/>Non avendone avuto risposto, credo conveniente
				<lb xml:id="p1-l10"/>di mandare ai medesimi ed a Lei, <choice><abbr>Preg<hi rend="sup">mo</hi> </abbr><expan>Pregiatissimo (Verehrtester)</expan></choice> <lb xml:id="p1-l11"/><choice><abbr>Sig.</abbr><expan>Signore (Herr)</expan></choice> Consigliere, copie del Capitolato, che
				<lb xml:id="p1-l12"/>comprende anche la concessione del tronco
				<lb xml:id="p1-l13"/><placeName key="Locarno">Locarno</placeName>–<placeName key="Biasca">Biasca</placeName>,
			</p>
      <p rend="left" xml:id="K_6656_p5"><lb xml:id="p1-l14"/>Se mai, nell'interesse dello scopo che si è prefisso
				<lb xml:id="p1-l15"/>il comitato del <placeName key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">Gottardo</placeName>, occorressero ulteriori
				<lb xml:id="p1-l16"/>informazioni od atti, mi troverò pronti ai
				<lb xml:id="p1-l17"/>suoi ordini.
			</p>
      <p rend="left" xml:id="K_6656_p6"><lb xml:id="p1-l18"/>Accolga, <choice><abbr>Preg<hi rend="sup">mo</hi> </abbr><expan>Pregiatissimo (Verehrtester)</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Sig<hi rend="sup">re</hi></abbr><expan>Signore (Herr)</expan></choice>, l'espressione di tutta la mia
				<lb xml:id="p1-l19"/>considerazione,
			</p>
    </body><back>
      <div type="closer">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_6656_p7"><lb xml:id="p1-l20"/>
          <choice><abbr>Dev<hi rend="sup">mo</hi> </abbr><expan>Devotissimo (ergebenst)</expan></choice> servo
			</p>
      </div>
      <div type="signature">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_6656_p8"><lb xml:id="p1-l21"/>Pasquale Veladini</p>
      </div>
    </back></text></TEI>